Additionally, it may belong to the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category as it deals with the behavior of individual neurons in a network. Finally, it may also belong to the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category as the techniques used in this paper could potentially be applied to understanding the features learned by neurons in language models.
